snippet.title: Offroad Truck Simulator: Heavy Duty Challenge | Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOW on PC, PS5 and Xbox Series X|S

Are you ready to discover the vast landscapes of Utah, a European forest and terrains in France, Poland, Austria and Iceland? Offroad Truck Simulator: Heavy Duty Challenge® gives you a whole new off-road experience with various huge and powerful trucks - available with the Mega Update - World of Cargo!

Store Pages: https://ots.aerosoft.com/

For more news and information follow us:
Discord: https://discord.gg/5g2PQK9K3x
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/heavydutychallenge/
